CustomField.description: Defines if the "Submit" button in the Timesheet Manager is available for use. If True, it will be hidden. When hidden, specific Users can be given access to use the button via the 'Enable Timesheet Manager Submit' field on the User object.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines if the "Submit" button in the Timesheet Manager is available for use. If True, it will be hidden. When hidden, specific Users can be given access to use the button via the 'Enable Timesheet Manager Submit' field on the User object.
CustomField.label: Hide Timesheet Manager Submit
